.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-8-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, light-blue, pink, apricot
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, cooking, chess, drawing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, romance, satire, superhero
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, french, indonesian, turkish
4 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, goldfish, rabbit
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, november, march, april
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, ship, tram
 1. the person watching fantasy movies is not the person who likes orange##6
 2. the owner of the rabbit is in an even position##4
 3. the person driving the ship is not to the right of the owner of the goldfish##8
 4. the person watching satire movies is the person driving the ship##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
 6. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
 7. the person watching superhero movies is not the person who likes apricot##6
 8. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5
 9. the owner of the bird is not to the right of the person watching superhero movies##8
10. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
11. the person who's hobby is chess is not to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##8
12. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
13. the turkish is not to the right of the person who likes pink##8
14. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3
15. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
16. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not to the left of the owner of the goldfish##8
17. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the turkish##1
18. the person who likes apricot is between the person watching fantasy movies and the french##2
19. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
20. the person who likes pink is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
21. the egyptian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##8
22. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the egyptian##1
23. the owner of the rabbit is not to the left of the person driving the ship##8
24. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
25. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the left of the person watching satire movies##8
26. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
27. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
28. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who likes pink##3
29. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5

