The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, golf, skateboarding, cycling
4 different pets are kept: cat, pony, rabbit, rat
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, pink, blood-red, white
 1. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who likes blood-red##1
 2. the owner of the pony is not to the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##8
 3. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 4. the person who's hobby is camping is the person drinking 7up##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is not the person eating apple##6
 6. the owner of the pony is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 7. the person who's hobby is gardening is not to the right of the person eating apple##8
 8. the person who's hobby is camping is not the person who likes brown##6
 9. the person drinking 7up is not the person who likes brown##6
10. the owner of the rat is not to the left of the person who's hobby is singing##8
11. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
12. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##8
13. the person who likes white is somewhere to the left of the person eating apple##5
14. the person eating orange is not the person who's hobby is camping##6
15. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##8
16. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5
17. the person eating raspberry is somewhere between the person eating apple and the person who's hobby is chess##7
18. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
19. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
20. the person drinking soy-milk is the owner of the rabbit##1
21. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
22. the person eating orange is the person who likes blood-red##1
23. the person who's birthday is in november is not to the left of the person eating mango##8
24. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who likes white##1
25. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
26. the person who likes pink is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
